    personal data to third parties if this is necessary within the scope of contract processing, for example to the
    credit institution entrusted with payment processing.
Further data transfer does not take
    place or only takes place if you have expressly consented to the transfer. Your data will not be passed on to third
    parties without your express consent, for example for advertising purposes.
