    the respective providers apply. The use of payment service providers is based on Art. 6 para. 1 lit. b GDPR
    (contract processing) and in the interest of a smooth, comfortable, and secure payment process (Art. 6 para. 1 lit.
    f GDPR). If your consent is requested for certain actions, Art. 6 para. 1 lit. a GDPR is the legal basis for data
    processing; consents can be revoked at any time.
